Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
  - 978
By: Sri Ramana Maharshi
---
The more you prune a plant, the more vigorously it grows. The more
you rectify your karma, the more it accumulates. Find the root of
karma and cut it.
